<br>
Make sure the raid force knows not to attack wretched.  Have your chanters have Mem blur handy.  Make sure your MA knows the difference between the 2.  As long as the MA has the right guy targeted and everyone is assisting correctly, there shouldn't be a problem.<br>
<br>
Everyone's assisting correctly, right?  *peers at the raid* <p>Zymyool, Officer of the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.ancientadventurers.org"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Ancient Adventurers</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> on the Karana Server<br>
